{"tid":6804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【姊弟戀血案】香港女歌手涉鎅傷前男友 身份大曝光","createTime":"2016-11-27T14:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T16:15:37.000Z","uid":16128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd412f193642477493e92ea6b1be7b1e792c55be","tid":6804,"uid":16128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"大埔發生姊弟戀鎅面血案，25歲青年與年長6歲長髮女友近日分手，女方今日清晨到男方寓所企圖「箍煲」復合不成，用鎅刀割手臂自殘，混亂中再涉嫌鎅傷前男友左臉，事後被警方拘捕( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2fnSJdT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2fnSJdT&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2FsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=87587e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2fnSJdT</a> )。<br />\n<br />\n被捕31歲姓張女子，是一名歌手，她於2009年出道，曾參加過不少歌唱比賽，同年曾於《超級巨聲》中擔任表演嘉賓，兩年後北上發展，參加中國音樂金鐘獎流行音樂大賽，獲得全國第5名以及最具音樂潛力獎，近年專注中港兩地演出。張不時拍下唱歌片放上YouTube及fb分享，去年曾在入境署就職典禮中獻唱，亦曾在香港一酒廊任駐唱歌手。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》晚上致電張女的經理人，他向記者表示「正處理法律程序」，惟未有正面回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161127&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=55974225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161127%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D55974225&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2FsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=e306f0d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161127%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D55974225&h=2b5dbcc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161127&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=55974225</a>"},{"pid":"bb8cc261d0cb73c8c30b87eb33c8cfc66ecb819a","tid":6804,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a9289576973d1b4b07ea38da63e36160cdd52fa","tid":6804,"uid":6844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"x可凝"},{"pid":"21e4e5c1e171e833a53f215365db755c462fd6b5","tid":6804,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"邊個姓張